column5: Nakina North had a cancellation. June 23-30, Percy Lake. A good sized lake with pike and walleye and miles of navigable river downstream for brook trout. $650 CAD plus hst for min party of 4. That's $502 US plus taxhttps://www.nakinanorthoutfitters.ca/percy-lake/
Hmmm, walleye & pike fillet fattened up on brook trout. Sounds like aquatic equivalent of free ranging grass fed beef.
pretty much, lol there was 2 discounted cancellation weeks, my party took one, I just thought I'd share in case somebody could take advantage of the other week
**** of a deal. Wish I could go. Sent from my Pixel 2 XL using Tapatalk
